[Israel has had multiple outbreaks of foot and mouth disease recently
in 2007 and 2009, according to the OIE WAHID database. For the
location of the outbreak see the OIE WAHID report referenced above or
see the Healthmap website. For a detailed report on these outbreaks
see the official Israeli report & Mod.AS commentary in ref. (03)
below. - Mod.PC]
